---
title: Chorizo, Egg, and Avocado Sandwich with a Chorizo Potato Onion Hash
description: Wakey, wakey, it’s eggs and … chorizo? Yep, we’re spicing up breakfast time with Spain’s most famous sausage. It adds paprika-laced flavor to this eggy sandwich on a brioche bun, as well as to the crispy, skillet-fried potato hash that’s on the side. A few slices of avocado on top are the finishing touch that makes this a perfect meal for powering through your day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-egg-and-avocado-breakfast-sandwich-f80863b6.jpg
